==English==
===Definition===

<b>forever</b> (<i>adverb</i>)

'''Forever''' means for an [[infinite]] amount of time. It is sometimes used synonomously with [[always]] or [[incessant|incessantly]], and also with [[continual|continually]]. An informal use of the term is to mean a very long time, as opposed to an infinite amount of time.

